## Run locally (optional)

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
export TWELVE_DATA_API_KEY="your_key"
export DISCORD_WEBHOOK_URL="your_webhook"
python main.py
```

Test the logic offline with no API key or Discord:

```bash
python test_offline.py
```

